---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { skills } from "../data/projects";
---

<BaseLayout title="About â€” la-bu" description="A little bit about me.">
  <div class="page">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1>About</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="hero">
      <div class="text">
        <h2>Servus, I'm Lars.</h2>
        <p>
          Fullstack dev based in Stuttgart. <br /><br />

          At work I write Java and TypeScript, translate business needs into actual software, and bridge the gap between dev teams,
          project leads, and customers. It's the kind of work I genuinely enjoy and there's something satisfying about making things
          click together.<br /><br />

          Outside of work, I have too many interests and not enough hours in the day which means life never gets boring ðŸ˜Š <br />
          The constants: lifting weights, running, eating well, and generally trying to feel good in my own skin.<br />
          Then there's everything else that comes and goes depending on the season or whatever I'm currently obsessed with. Music production,
          alpine hiking, skiing, audiophile rabbit holes, building furniture, traveling, and tinkering with side projects like this blog.
          <br />
          The music production one always catches people off guard. I actually did it professionally for two years after school before I
          decided it wasn't the life I wanted and made the deliberate switch to software. Still make music though, just for myself now.
          <br />
          This blog is a mix of whatever I feel like writing about. Tech posts when I learn something worth sharing, music nerd stuff when
          I'm deep in a rabbit hole, travel logs, build diaries, random thoughts. No strict format, just things I want to put out into the
          world.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="photo-placeholder" aria-hidden="true">
        {/* Replace this div with an <img> once you have a photo */}
      </div>
    </div>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Tech Stack</h2>
      <div class="skills-groups">
        {
          skills.map((group) => (
            <ul class="tag-list">
              {group.map((skill) => (
                <li class="tag">{skill}</li>
              ))}
            </ul>
          ))
        }
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-6);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-10);
  }

  .page-header h1 {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
  }

  .hero {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 280px;
    gap: var(--space-12);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .photo-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 3 / 4;
    background-color: var(--color-bg-subtle);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 6px;
  }

  .section {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .skills-groups {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .page {
      padding: var(--space-8) var(--space-4);
      gap: var(--space-8);
    }

    .hero {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .photo-placeholder {
      aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;
      max-width: 240px;
    }
  }
</style>
